Class DirectoryConfig

  • Object
    • DirectoryConfig

  • public class DirectoryConfig
extends Object
    This class provides an overview of Configs related to specific files and folders.
    Author:
    Mythic_Freak - mythic.freak[a]gmail.com *
    Note
    These configs typically require a (re-)start to take effect.
